# Cloudflare config — wrangler.jsonc (standalone, PLACEHOLDER ids) IS committed as the
# public OSS / one-click-deploy default (CF auto-provisions resources + injects real ids).
# Real ids / private configs live in gitignored variant files:
#   wrangler.local.jsonc — your real standalone ids (scripts/setup-cloudflare.js writes it)
#   wrangler.saas.jsonc  — InspectorHub private SaaS config
wrangler.*.jsonc
wrangler.toml
wrangler.*.toml

